# Production URL for canonical links and social preview images
# SITE_URL=https://your-domain.com

# ── Decap CMS ──
# Full guide: docs/decap-setup.md
#
# By default the live /admin CMS is browse-only (dashboard + entries, no saves).
# To enable editing on your deployment:
#   1. Set PUBLIC_DECAP_REPO to your fork (username/repo)
#   2. Configure GitHub OAuth on your host (see docs/decap-setup.md)
#   3. Set PUBLIC_DECAP_EDIT_ENABLED=true
#
# PUBLIC_DECAP_EDIT_ENABLED=true
# PUBLIC_DECAP_REPO=your-username/your-fork
# PUBLIC_DECAP_TEMPLATE_REPO=https://github.com/faruqso/kujera-furniture-starter
